{"type": "article", "id": 2234, "title": "沙筑灯", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T23:26:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222259DqY9QoeM2FLIuCG0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tSustainable Sand Light by<a href=\"http://alienandmonkey.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Alien and Monkey </a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这款沙筑灯的原料来自自然界最常见的材质之一，沙，设计师利用传统制陶技术发明了新的材质。有趣的是，像点燃的蜡烛一样，随着时间的流逝，灯的形状会因腐蚀而不断改变，最后这款灯会完全消失，而这个过程所产生的所有物质都是可以自然降解的。相比于其他灯具，短暂的存在反而让这款灯拥有了生命。<a href=\"http://alienandmonkey.com/contact/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里联系购买。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072613512878ZKHQCz2T0ySj1u.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135129AnxKMQcrLbIepyUP.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135129UuYEIrGd0phWj9HC.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}